<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>may contain <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:No_original_research" title="Wikipedia:No original research">original research</a> or <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Verifiability" title="Wikipedia:Verifiability">unverified claims</a></b>. Please <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Indian_English&amp;action=edit" class="external text" title="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Indian_English&amp;action=edit" rel="nofollow">improve the article</a> by adding <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:References" title="Wikipedia:References" class="mw-redirect">references</a>. See the <a href="/wiki/Talk:Indian_English" title="Talk:Indian English">talk page</a> for details. <small><i>(February 2008)</i></small></td>
